Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:04.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,First time ever on Gaki no Tsukai ya Arahende...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:07.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,..."Who is the most convincing?" Self-health presentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:15.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know this already, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:18.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...out of the five of us, I'm the smartest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:23.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Today we'll see how much of it I can show it off to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:29.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,We all drifted off, somewhere far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That means that none of us are convinced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:34.44,Hosei,,0,0,0,,...of him being that smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:36.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:38.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We'll now be given the subjects to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We have a library at our disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We'll compile materials and give a presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First the health-related subjects are decided with a lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,High Blood Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is going to be complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't have the faintest idea about high blood pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}T/N: Background music is "Winter Winner" by Orange Range
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Hamada got aging prevention...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Yamasaki got hip pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Endo got summer fatigue...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:07.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and Tanaka got bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What kind of presentations will they give?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:13.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To study about their subjects...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:15.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...they went to a library to gather materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We can't be too loud here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of the Silent Library series.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:23.41,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That brings back bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:25.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:30.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The search for materials to study begins right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can't go without checking this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:47.13,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm at a dead end already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,I am completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to approach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Don't know at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:06.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Endo be able to find the materials he needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, his partner Tanaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:12.02,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Bad breath bye-bye! Bad breath bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.22,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Bad breath bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hamada has also finally found something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Can I take these with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After gathering the materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...they proceed to making the presentations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:08.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Gaki members are unusually serious about their presentations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:17.50,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"...this survey was done on 288 people by Kanebo..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}T/N: Kanebo is a major cosmetic brand in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:24.33,Endo,,0,0,0,,"...raise your feet to a 90 degree angle and do this..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:37.23,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I've never drawn a picture like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Never ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.93,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Hamada's picture be completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to give the presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Everyone, are you feeling a bit tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:10.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We had about two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:14.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I ran out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm usually better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I study more before doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.02,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well let's just do the presentations already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tanaka is the top batter.  He has the subject of "bad breath".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:38.22,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,This spring, two subordinates come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:41.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,But you can only hire one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:48.02,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,They both have equal looks, ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.02,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...judgment, and character.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:54.12,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,However, one of them has bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:57.36,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,The other does not have bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:59.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,In that case, which one do you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.04,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, Hamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If at all possible, the one without bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.98,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Bad breath can cause problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.98,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...in school...at work...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:13.16,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...or at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What is this bumbling, are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.86,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I'd now like to talk to you about bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.45,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Your introduction was so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:26.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Two meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,What do you think this distance is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.99,Hosei,,0,0,0,,How far bad breath reaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.14,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:41.42,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Did you really have to cover that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:46.42,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I'd like to do an experiment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.21,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,A bad breath check you can easily do at home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I'll give each of you a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You prepared all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Breathe into the cup, and put your hand over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Then, take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:09.65,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Now, sniff the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.22,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Can you detect your own bad breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:20.27,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It kind of stunk when I took the deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.51,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to look at this flipcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:29.85,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Kanebo did this study in 1994 to men and women aged 18 to 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That survey is damn old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:32.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,More than 10 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.82,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Teacher! I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:41.10,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Let's just look at it, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.10,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Who cares, it's 12 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ideas might have changed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.52,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Smells people like!  Third is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...freshly baked bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't think too many people say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:54.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.46,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:01.36,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And number one is soap's natural scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Because Kanebo did the survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's the Pink Lady era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}T/N: Pink Lady was a female pop music duo popular in the late 70s and early 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.84,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And now...bad smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's not that old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Third most hated is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.06,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...body odor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.33,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Number two is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.74,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...kitchen waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And of course number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.12,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...is bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I could see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:27.61,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Bad breath ranks higher than kitchen waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Have a look at this other flipcard too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:36.15,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,The drug company Nihon Kayaku, in 1990...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:36.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's even older!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.19,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You lose interest right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:45.26,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Of course, number one is... bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:48.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's the subject, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.32,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And bad breath is number one for women, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:53.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,Wow, about eight out of ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:58.18,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's right.  Eight out of ten people, both men and women, hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:00.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But it's from 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:03.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,The question is, "who is a partner I would not want to marry?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What's the point in covering them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.32,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"Somebody whose mouth stinks."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is the theme, we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:13.02,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,How many visits to the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.02,Tanaka,,0,0,0,, ...does it take to get rid of bad breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:20.18,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Can it be healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:21.56,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yes. Depending on the treatment, you can cure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,How many times do you think, Endo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.83,Endo,,0,0,0,,Five times?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:28.42,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,I got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's pretty embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.38,Endo,,0,0,0,,I got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.22,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He looked really annoyed just then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.38,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's the end of my presentation on bad breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up is Yamasaki who is full of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His subject is "hip pain."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,My subject is "hip pain."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,When you think of hip pain, what image do you conjure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:04.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what the hell you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:07.80,Hosei,,0,0,0,,When you hear "hip pain," what does it make you think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.11,Endo,,0,0,0,,Old age, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:14.82,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Well, old age ... and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell was the point of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:21.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You should show us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm so envious of gags like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,We can divide hip pain into three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Let's look at this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:38.88,Hosei,,0,0,0,,(Blank) on the hip exceeds its strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.88,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, what is placed on the hip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.91,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Umm... Stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:43.91,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.86,Endo,,0,0,0,,We got another one right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.03,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Number two...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.46,Hosei,,0,0,0,,...the (blank) itself is abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,How about it, Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.38,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.38,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,...the hip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,It fit in there so perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.94,Endo,,0,0,0,,It was the only reasonable answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You should at least try to hide the length of the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.86,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,...at who is at highest risk of having hip problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Everyday life ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,This was quite interesting to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "everyday life?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.82,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,When you live your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is it about when you might get hip problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.18,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Where excessive stress is placed on the hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.62,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Night shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.62,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's when it's easy to get pain in the hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Especially men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Let's have number two.  What do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:45.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Washing the dishes, or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:45.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Washing the dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.43,Hosei,,0,0,0,,...is actually number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:50.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Household chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:55.65,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Housewives are right up there at number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:00.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well now I don't care about number two any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.96,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,We don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.33,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.83,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Playing."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you mean, "playing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}(* - This is Yamasaki's own ranking and has no basis in reality.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:14.50,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yama-chan's "You Gotta Remember This!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.74,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You have to memorize...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,, ...what's best in foodstuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.03,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:27.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Vitamin B and calcium are good for hips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.75,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What do you think is best, among foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Eggs are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:34.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,What about cheese?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Endo is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.42,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That ripped off really cleanly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why did you hide the entire card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Today, on this special occasion, I've brought cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We've all seen cheese before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't need to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.40,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,We know what cheese is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.54,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's the end of my hip pain presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:21.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up is Endo, who had trouble in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His subject is "summer fatigue."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Out of the five of us, he's the problem child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:35.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Hello.  I'd like to tell you about summer fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.58,Endo,,0,0,0,,When you hear "summer fab-... summer fatigue"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.34,Endo,,0,0,0,,...summer fatigue...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the issue on a planetary scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's a big scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.88,Endo,,0,0,0,,What's El Niño?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:57.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,You have some sort of an idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Well, I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:02.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,El Niño is a phenomenon in South America...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.19,Endo,,0,0,0,,...where on Ecuador and Peru's coast...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:09.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,...every 4-5 years, sea temperatures rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,You have the explanation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,330)}So you just copied that text.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:16.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to understand this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He just keeps turning the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can't memorize anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:25.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,Just look at this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.06,Endo,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.06,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Summer fatigue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.38,Endo,,0,0,0,,The El Niño phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What's the point in covering that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:39.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,It changes the atmospheric currents...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.54,Endo,,0,0,0,,...and causes what around the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:42.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,What comes before low temperatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.37,Endo,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san?  Before low temperatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well, not before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.88,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,High temperatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:56.02,Endo,,0,0,0,,It causes high and low temperatures, rains and drought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:59.10,Endo,,0,0,0,,...which causes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Calamities?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:01.10,Endo,,0,0,0,,Abnormal weather conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.27,Endo,,0,0,0,,El Niño causes abnormal weather conditions right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:06.90,Endo,,0,0,0,,Abnormal weather conditions mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:11.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,...winters are getting colder all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.42,Endo,,0,0,0,,Summers are getting hotter and hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.35,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\clip(108.169,433,317.496,492)}When it gets hot, what fatigue is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,When it gets hot, what fatigue is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That took forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Summer fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,You get summer fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.62,Endo,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about summer fatigue now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.23,Endo,,0,0,0,,Here's a health check-up list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'll go from number one to number ten for everyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:35.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'll read these, and if one fits you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,...please remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your eyes tire easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your shoulders and back are stiff. Yours, right, Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.26,Endo,,0,0,0,,You tire easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,You have nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your face twitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.30,Endo,,0,0,0,,You lack appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your hands tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Your feet and hands feel cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,You can't think straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's "palpitations".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,Palpitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:01.46,Endo,,0,0,0,,You experience palpitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.97,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's obvious he just copied the text.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.97,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He didn't read it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I had about two fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Two for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.16,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I have three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,Zero to one means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,...good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:19.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We're all in the second group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,Let's look at four to six then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,Needs attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.30,Endo,,0,0,0,,Seven or more is very worrisome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:29.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Worrying about summer fatigue, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,Two to three is the average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell, man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We don't need to know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,When you get summer fatigue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,...you lose your appetite and stop eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,The molecules that store energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:47.91,Endo,,0,0,0,,...do you know what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,Gly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Glycogen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.70,Endo,,0,0,0,,It forms glycogen and stores it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.50,Endo,,0,0,0,,It has a deciphering effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's "detoxification"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.90,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about encryption!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:11.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm so envious of mistakes like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,At last, Matsumoto's presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.83,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His theme is "high blood pressure".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:28.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be joking even half the time from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,First, a simple problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What is the connection between these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, "high", of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:48.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I could tell you about any one of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.82,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...but today let's look at high blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:55.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sooo... Tokyo University's circulatory organ clinic's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:17:00.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...diagnosis chief Yasunobu Hirata...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...has done research about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What do you think these are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is the number of people affected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...by high blood pressure in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,35 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Only approximately, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's no point in covering that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What's that about the FBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,FBI, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:36.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who decides the basis for the diagnosis of high blood pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Number one is FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Number two, PTA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Number three is the WHO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.22,Endo,,0,0,0,,We know it can't be the PTA or FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.22,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the end, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.90,Hosei,,0,0,0,,We don't need this any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you put the same amount of water through...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...a stiff, narrow hose - compared to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.90,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...an elastic, thick hose, the narrow hose...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...spews water with a higher force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is the principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:15.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The more narrow it is, the higher the pressure gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I've explained it in simple terms with a rubber hose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It can also be shown with jeans.  Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So you really have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of text.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:41.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Internal secretions regulate the blood pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:45.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...through autonomic nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.98,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is how they're related to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:52.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If you just look at this, you'll pretty much understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.30,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Various things result in high blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Get this through your thick heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.22,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Could you explain it a bit further?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If we think about it in terms of Yoshimoto comedians...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}T/N: Yoshimoto is the agency that Downtown, Hosei, and Cocorico work for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:06.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'll name it the difference between rich and poor people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well, they resemble each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.86,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:16.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You can't show it too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It disappeared so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:25.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything else to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.46,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\clip(145.227,434,264.413,480)}What is... this solemn feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:36.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What is... this solemn feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:44.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hamada finishes up with aging prevention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,My subject is "aging prevention".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We're all steadily aging.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we all relate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:01.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We are all getting older.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,First up - what is aging?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:11.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's aged so much he can't insert the flipcard properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is aging. Read it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:24.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Along with aging, internal organs' functions gradually deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:28.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eventually you become unable to cope with your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:34.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's a process that leads to death, and it advances all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.70,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...being irreversible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:39.30,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:39.30,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:45.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When does aging really start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:50.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,One by one.  Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When does aging start?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Teacher, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's hard for me to think like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.54,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,When you're 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.45,Hamada,,0,0,0,,40, ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:04.14,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's aging, so I'll say 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,50? OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.84,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I think 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I also think it's pretty early...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...so I'll take the middle ground and say 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.87,Hamada,,0,0,0,,One of you got it right.  It starts at the age of 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes, from the age of 20, aging has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.82,0:21:21.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What is the phenomenon of aging?  Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.58,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Aging is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:29.40,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's like that guy from Dengeki Network.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}T/N: Dengeki Network was a group of four men who were known for performing dangerous stunts.  They were popular in the 1990s.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(125.195,390)}Dengeki Network
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(123.192,431)}Nanbu Torata
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:34.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nanbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:40.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Dementia, cataracts, diabetes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:43.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...bones and muscles deteriorate, balding and gray hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:46.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...wrinkles, high blood pressure like we had earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:48.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...and the decline of reproductive functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,This is what aging is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:53.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His pace is quite fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:53.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:56.82,Hamada,,0,0,0,,After middle age, what are the abilities that get better...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...and the ones that get worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:02.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There are abilities that actually improve?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:07.11,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Memory improves with age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:09.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,These are the abilities that improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:13.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Imagination, analysis, judgement and thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.55,0:22:15.84,Hosei,,0,0,0,,They're all intellect-based.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When you get older, these actually go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.79,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Things like learning ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There are the abilities that deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:27.77,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Memorization, long-term memory and concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.74,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:33.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,However, even if you become unable to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:35.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...do tricky calculations in your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:37.94,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...you can still live a good life...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:39.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...as long as you have good judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:22:41.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if some abilities deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:44.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's what the proverb "the older, the wiser" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why did you write that in brown?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.74,0:22:54.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Out of all the colors you chose that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.56,0:23:03.32,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Bones and muscles deteriorate.  Let's concentrate on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:06.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How old are you in terms of elasticity?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:11.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If you're in your 20s, you should be able to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:15.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Both your hands can touch the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:20.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...and your face can reach your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:24.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The arms and legs are way out of proportion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,In your 40s the tips of your fingers reach the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Lastly, in your 50s...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:39.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,, ...your fingers are further than 20 cm from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.78,Endo,,0,0,0,,I'm probably in the 50s.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:42.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The man in the illustration is moving further from the foreground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:49.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If you think about your elasticity, how old would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:52.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't have any confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:52.74,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Me too, I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.74,0:23:54.94,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So everyone is in this group?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.94,0:23:56.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Your fingers can't reach the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:59.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, mine somehow reaches the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:23:59.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:01.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:04.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We're all in our 50s!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:06.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So, aging is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:11.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We don't need that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:13.14,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:16.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:19.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,We talked about this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is like the main menu of a video game.
